outh Slough NERR by visiting researchers. This proposal seeks $60,000 in order to add 500 sq. ft. of laboratory sp  ace to the new Estuarine and Coastal Research Laboratory for use by scientists visiting OIMB.  \par \sect }\sectd \sbknone\linex0 \pard\plain  4 s20 { 5 s22   \par }}
